Integrated Project “Rue Gray-Maelbeek” (Brussels, Belgium) (2 weeks Project)
Drainage Modelling (Vrije Universiteit Brussel) 
▪ Developed an EPA-SWMM model for an unconnected 
  pipe network and integrated it into the city's main sewer 
  system. 
▪ Simulated a high-precipitation event (July 9th storm) to 
  identify and analyze the origins of flooding locations. 
▪ Validated model results against citizen-observed flood 
  data.
